    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722349,
    "reference_id": 19208,
    "title": "Lamentations 3.34–36",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003034-25003036",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Les habitants de Juda faisaient de telles choses avant que Jérusalem ne soit détruite (voir <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:26-Jer5:31\">Jr&nbsp;5.26–31</a>&nbsp;; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer21:11-Jer21:14\">21.11–14</a>&nbsp;; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:10-Jer23:14\">23.10–14</a>&nbsp;; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:1-Mic3:12\">Mi&nbsp;3</a>).</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003034",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:34",
          "end_ref": "25003036",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:36"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722350,
    "reference_id": 19209,
    "title": "Lamentations 3.37–39",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003037-25003039",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Certaines calamités viennent de causes naturelles (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:1-Luke13:5\">Lc 13.1–5</a>), et des mauvaises choses arrivent aux justes comme aux méchants (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:45\">Mt&nbsp;5.45</a>)&nbsp;; quoi qu’il arrive, il faut rendre grâces (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:18\">1Th&nbsp;5.18</a>) et ne pas se plaindre.</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003037",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:37",
          "end_ref": "25003039",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:39"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722351,
    "reference_id": 19210,
    "title": "Lamentations 3.40–42",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003040-25003042",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Le repentir est la clé pour recevoir le salut (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:27\">Es&nbsp;1.27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:22\">Jr 3.22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:21\">Ez&nbsp;3.21</a>).</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003040",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:40",
          "end_ref": "25003042",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:42"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722352,
    "reference_id": 19211,
    "title": "Lamentations 3.48–66",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003048-25003066",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>L’auteur se concentre sur la cruauté des ennemis et s’écrie vers le Seigneur pour obtenir de l’aide.</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003048",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:48",
          "end_ref": "25003066",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:66"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722353,
    "reference_id": 19212,
    "title": "Lamentations 3.52–57",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003052-25003057",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Ce passage peut renvoyer à l’expérience de Jérémie dans la citerne (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:11-Jer37:15\">Jr 37.11–15 </a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:1-Jer38:13\">38.1–13</a>).</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003052",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:52",
          "end_ref": "25003057",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:57"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722354,
    "reference_id": 19213,
    "title": "Lamentations 3.58–66",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003058-25003066",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Jérusalem méritait une punition, mais ses ennemis l’ont exécutée avec une cruauté injustifiée. L’auteur en appelle à Dieu pour les punir.</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003058",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:58",
          "end_ref": "25003066",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:66"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722356,
    "reference_id": 19215,
    "title": "Lamentations 3.64–66",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25003064-25003066",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Cette prière pour la vengeance est similaire à plusieurs psaumes (voir la note thématique «&nbsp;<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"203217\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotesThemes\">Prières pour la vengeance</span>&nbsp;»).</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25003064",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:64",
          "end_ref": "25003066",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 3:66"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722358,
    "reference_id": 19217,
    "title": "Lamentations 4.1–22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004001-25004022",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Bien que le peuple de Dieu subisse encore son jugement, il connaîtra bientôt la rédemption.</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:1",
          "end_ref": "25004022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722365,
    "reference_id": 19224,
    "title": "Lamentations 4.3",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004003",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Comme les autruches&nbsp;: Voir aussi <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job39:13-Job39:16\">Jb&nbsp;39.13–16</a>.</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:3",
          "end_ref": "25004003",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:3"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722366,
    "reference_id": 19225,
    "title": "Lamentations 4.7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004007",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>comme le saphir&nbsp;: Le saphir est une belle pierre bleue, assez malléable pour être sculptée. On l’utilise souvent dans les décorations et les mosaïques.</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:7",
          "end_ref": "25004007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722367,
    "reference_id": 19226,
    "title": "Lamentations 4.8",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004008",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>La peau collée sur les os est symptomatique des stades finaux de la famine, juste avant la mort.</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004008",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:8",
          "end_ref": "25004008",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:8"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722368,
    "reference_id": 19227,
    "title": "Lamentations 4.9",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004009",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Les longs sièges entraînent une grave pénurie de nourriture. Même si les gens pouvaient se rendre aux champs, ils trouveraient les cultures détruites ou déjà récoltées pour nourrir les soldats.</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:9",
          "end_ref": "25004009",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:9"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722359,
    "reference_id": 19218,
    "title": "Lamentations 4.12",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004012",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Les rois de la terre n’auraient pas cru… entrerait Dans les portes de Jérusalem&nbsp;: Depuis que Dieu avait délivré Jérusalem de Sanchérib d’Assyrie plus d’un siècle auparavant (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:36-2Kgs19:37\">2R&nbsp;19.36–37</a>), les Judéens croyaient fermement que même le plus puissant roi, Nabuchodonosor de Babylone, ne pouvait vaincre la ville.</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:12",
          "end_ref": "25004012",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:12"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722360,
    "reference_id": 19219,
    "title": "Lamentations 4.15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004015",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Il semble que ces chefs aient fui Jérusalem en tant que réfugiés vers d’autres contrées.</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:15",
          "end_ref": "25004015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722361,
    "reference_id": 19220,
    "title": "Lamentations 4.20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004020",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Celui... A été pris dans leurs fosses&nbsp;: Il s’agit d’une référence à Sédécias, qui a essayé de fuir mais a été capturé et traité cruellement par Nebucadnetsar (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:4-2Kgs25:7\">2R 25.4–7</a> ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer39:4-Jer39:7\">Jr 39.4–7</a> ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:9-Jer52:11\">52.9–11</a>).</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004020",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:20",
          "end_ref": "25004020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722363,
    "reference_id": 19222,
    "title": "Lamentations 4.21",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004021",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Uts était une région à l’est du Jourdain qui s’étendait au sud jusqu’à Édom. C’était le domicile de Job (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:1\">Jb&nbsp;1.1</a>).</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004021",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:21",
          "end_ref": "25004021",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:21"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722362,
    "reference_id": 19221,
    "title": "Lamentations 4.21–22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004021-25004022",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Les habitants d’Édom se sentaient en sécurité et se réjouissaient du malheur de Jérusalem, mais eux aussi subiraient une punition pour leurs péchés (voir <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:1-Obad1:21\">Ab&nbsp;1</a>&nbsp;; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer49:7-Jer49:22\">Jr 49.7–22</a>).</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004021",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:21",
          "end_ref": "25004022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722364,
    "reference_id": 19223,
    "title": "Lamentations 4.22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25004022",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Le premier retour d’exil a eu lieu en 538 av. J.‑C., après la victoire de Cyrus de Perse face à Babylone (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:22-2Chr36:23\">2Ch&nbsp;36.22–23</a>&nbsp;; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra1:1-Ezra1:4\">Esd&nbsp;1.1–4</a>).</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25004022",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:22",
          "end_ref": "25004022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 4:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722369,
    "reference_id": 19228,
    "title": "Lamentations 5.1–22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25005001-25005022",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Ce chapitre est une prière sincère pour le repentir (cf. <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:4-Dan9:19\">Dn&nbsp;9.4–19</a>).</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25005001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:1",
          "end_ref": "25005022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722370,
    "reference_id": 19229,
    "title": "Lamentations 5.10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25005010",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Il y avait une famine dans la ville pendant le siège (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:3\">2R 25.3 </a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:21\">Jr 37.21 </a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:9\">38.9 </a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:6\">52.6</a>).</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25005010",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:10",
          "end_ref": "25005010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722371,
    "reference_id": 19230,
    "title": "Lamentations 5.12–17",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25005012-25005017",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>Ces événements terribles sont survenus parce que le peuple avait péché (voir <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:7-Isa24:12\">Es 24.7–12</a>&nbsp;; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:24\">Jr 7.24</a> ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:18\">13.18</a> ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:10-Jer25:11\">25.10–11</a> ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:10\">Am 8.10</a>).</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25005012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:12",
          "end_ref": "25005017",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:17"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 722372,
    "reference_id": 19231,
    "title": "Lamentations 5.18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "25005018",
    "language": "fra",
    "content": "<p>les renards s&apos;y promènent : Cf. <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa13:22\">Es 13.22</a>&nbsp;; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:13\">34.13</a>&nbsp;; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:11\">Jr 9.11 </a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:22\">10.22 </a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:3\">Ml&nbsp;1.3</a>.</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "25005018",
          "start_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:18",
          "end_ref": "25005018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "LAM 5:18"
        }
